@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bwaxrw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.75 + v1 + 0.31) * (v2 + 0.22 - v1 + 0.02)))
    tmp = (0.09 + wp.abs(0.84))
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v2 + 0.09) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.39)))
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
